<view class="page theme-toolbox toolbox-page paper-page">
  <view class="page-head floral-title-box drawer-head title-pattern-card"><image class="title-pattern-image" src="/assets/title-patterns/deep-purple.png" mode="aspectFill" /><view class="title-pattern-mask"></view>
    <view class="corner-ornament corner-ornament-left corner-ornament--gold"></view>
    <view class="corner-ornament corner-ornament-right corner-ornament--green"></view>
    <text class="eyebrow">精致工具抽屉</text>
    <text class="hero-title">吗喽的百宝箱</text>
    <text class="subtext">泡泡机、呼吸、自测、急救卡片和出走小技能，都先收在这个小抽屉里。</text>
  </view>



  <view class="tool-grid">
    <view wx:for="{{items}}" wx:key="title" class="tool-card ornament-card ornament-card--gold {{item.color}}" data-index="{{index}}" bindtap="openTool">
      <view class="corner-ornament corner-ornament-left corner-ornament--gold"></view>
      <view class="paper-corner bottom-right"></view>
      <text class="tool-title">{{item.title}}</text>
      <text class="subtext">{{item.subtitle}}</text>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="feedback-note note-card paper-edge" bindtap="openFeedback">
    <view class="paper-corner right"></view>
    <text class="feedback-title">试用反馈</text>
    <text>帮吗喽捡一点小树枝，让这个王国慢慢变好。</text>
  </view>
</view>
